                                           BUSINESS QUESTION
Are users with better focus scores also having better mood scores? 

                 QUERY
SELECT
  focus_score,
  mood_score
FROM mental_health
ORDER BY focus_score,
mood_score DESC;

Insight:
For someone to have a good focus, he or she must be in a good mood 

Recommendation:
Improving focus (less distraction) can improve emotional wellbeing.
